title: TikTok star and activist Shirley Raines of Beauty 2 the Streetz dies at 58
summary_full: Shirley Raines, known as Ms. Shirley and founder of Beauty 2 the Streetz, has died at 58. She gained popularity on TikTok for her work providing beauty and hygiene services to unhoused communities in Los Angeles and Nevada. Her passing was confirmed by her organization, which highlighted her tireless advocacy and the lasting impact she made.
